snippet.title: Angelina Jolie Defends Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard...!?
snippet.description:
Angelina Jolie Defends Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard...!? 
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's long-going court cases has brought in character witnesses and that meant bringing in many A-List stars to talk about Depp and Heard, and more recently, one of them has come out about trying to warn Depp about Heard. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at how Angelina Jolie apparently tried to warn Johnny Depp about Amber Heard, and the other celebrities and friends who have tried to defend him during his court case that's still ongoing. Do you think that it's odd that people believe Depp is an abuser and yet many of those he's worked with and been with say he's not? Do the words of these people hold enough weight to free Johnny in the end? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
